description:
Demolition of existing building and erection of 3 and 4 storey building to accommodate 40 sheltered flats (37 x one bedroom and 3 x two bedroom), day centre, 12 bedsits and communal accommodation for older people with 13 car parking spaces and amenity space. 

 APPLICANTS' PLAN NOS.:  Unnumbered existing site survey                         A587/2.1/01C - 04C, A587/2.1/5B as                         amended by street elevation on                         A587/4.1/08, A587/2.1/6A,                         A587/2.1/21.
decision_conditions:
CONDITION: The development hereby permitted shall be begun not later than the expiration of five years from the date of this permission. 

 REASON: To comply with the provisions of Section 91(1) of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
